com.salesforce.omakase.ast.collection

Interface SyntaxCollection<P,T extends Groupable<P,T>>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - Type of the (P)arent object containing this collection (e.g., SelectorParts have Selectors as the parent).
    T - The (T)ype of units to be grouped with.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedSyntaxCollection

    public interface SyntaxCollection<P,T extends Groupable<P,T>>
extends Iterable<T>
    A collection of related Syntax units.
